name: Comedian Twist Digital Reborn (2021)
description:
Experimental Tribute to Maurizio Cattelan and its questionably "genius" artwork Comedian (2019).

-3 artworks were released and displayed.
-2 sold for $120K USD.
-1 vandalized (eaten) by the performance artist David Datuna.

The floor price of these will be 120 XTZ, 3 editions.
They will endure the test of time decentralized on tezos chain. 
Digital artwork is supposedly non-perishable. 
So unlike Mauricio, I won't replace any lost nana ;)
